{"tid":983834,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東南亞五國之旅（處女post）","createTime":"2019-01-16T09:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T10:41:01.000Z","uid":231598,"like":31,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4d24b9038362700fa0fb16eee06d18f35a0939a2","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"序：<br />\n小弟剛剛辭左職同老婆打算周圍去，<br />\n所以開左個連登ac想打下遊記，俾自己記錄下。<br />\n成個plan其實都係冇乜plan，暫時去緊東南亞，之後想去南美（巴西、阿根廷、智利、玻利維亞、秘魯、maybe Ecuador）、埃及、摩洛哥、東西歐、俄羅斯。<br />\n大概個plan係咁，去度邊度止步就要睇下我地個荷包嘅深度了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭先開ac個時好似第一次上咸網咁，既興奮又緊張。<br />\n現正身處越南會安<br />\n今日落大雨冇乜地方去，所以留喺酒店打下文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVkSqvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVkSqvX.png&h=ff68a01c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係我地黎越南嘅Day4，<br />\n喺峴港落機，去左順化，再落到黎會安<br />\n之後嘅行程：大叻 -&gt; 美奈 -&gt; 胡志明<br />\n最後會喺清萊飛番香港。<br />\n<br />\n黎緊plan緊去柬埔寨、寮國、緬甸、同北泰（主要清邁）<br />\n呢個trip total 得38日，其實都係淺度遊。<br />\n之後會慢慢打下成個行程（希望唔好爛尾）"},{"pid":"a44c657ddc76c44b22ab74667eb0e7ac430558df","tid":983834,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"等睇南美"},{"pid":"5fabe4d7fa533f43c18e552cecdd2a03bdb8b20b","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a44c657ddc76c44b22ab74667eb0e7ac430558df","tid":983834,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"等睇南美"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"Sor第一次用連登<br />\n我有冇得edit自己個post架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e867406751f946601e526c9841a0cc008a338ee8","tid":983834,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fabe4d7fa533f43c18e552cecdd2a03bdb8b20b","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a44c657ddc76c44b22ab74667eb0e7ac430558df","tid":983834,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"等睇南美"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"Sor第一次用連登<br />\n我有冇得edit自己個post架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856626352d5076bc146286223e460d2e6c2cc6a4","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"Day1  香港 -&gt; <span style=\"color: maroon;\"></span>峴港<br />\n<br />\n當然係坐hkexpress，買到平飛票，去峴港清萊番7xx。因為去咁耐，所以都揹左個大Backpack，我就60+10L，佢就55L，但因為未試過咁大個袋上機，好驚到時先唔俾handcarry要每人加390寄倉（單程），加上我有個相機腳架（我又唔sure過唔過到安檢），所以自己預先加每一件275（單程），當張機票冇咁平就算。<br />\n點知去到機場，個地勤話呢啲backpack應該可以handcarry，問我地想寄倉定點，我再三問佢：真係得架？佢都幾firm話得，之後指住一個鐵框，話：你塞到入去就得架喇（唔係叫我塞自己入去）。<br />\n事後過安檢我都問工作人員，相機腳架香港機場係俾過嘅（但我試過台中唔得，另外上網睇番，台灣啲機場係比較嚴）。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅backpack<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tB6KgMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtB6KgMU.png&h=096cafcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCPDmdF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCPDmdF.png&h=2ee4735e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落左機喺機場冇兌VND，因為聽講唔扺<br />\n又搵唔到ATM，所以等入市區ATM撳錢<br />\n入市區call grab（類似uber嘅apps）<br />\n咁就可以冇VND都入到市區<br />\n其實身上有300美金，但喺東南亞洗美金多數都係唔扺，會收到你幾蚊到十幾蚊港幣不等。<br />\n所以用grab就可以用信用卡俾錢（匯率未check，之後會再講番兌錢用atm，credit卡兌錢扺唔扺）<br />\n（點解會用eps同credit card係因為之前去台灣呢兩個方法係比去找換店兌台幣扺好多，又方便，下次去你地可以try下）<br />\n本身要58000VND（~20HKD）去city，但唔知係咪第一次用，所以免費左。<br />\n小心啲越南司機，有人approach我地（佢知我地用緊grab叫車），話佢都係grab司機，收番grab嗰個價車我地，咁就唔洗用app咁煩，但我就奇怪佢show俾我睇嗰個錢係成百五蚊港幣，我都奇怪點解咁貴，原來grab有幾款車（eg 普通車，七人車等），佢揀左最貴個款俾我地睇，好彩我地冇上當。<br />\nGrab幾好用，用左幾次，佢明碼實價講定幾錢，又用credit card俾錢，全程唔洗同人bargain（最憎同人講價），之後又會收到email receipt，又有得set 緊急聯絡人/撳emergency button，所以個人認為比喺街搭的士安全啲。"},{"pid":"58cbb02392ac3270d8ec2364249783cf93d9d298","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"Day1 （住過最平嘅酒店）<br />\n你地最平住過幾錢？<br />\n明明越南酒店出名平靚正<br />\n一百幾十蚊就有個公眾泳池<br />\n偏偏我地就試下住平野。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ffi5NV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ffi5NV.png&h=6480084c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m01immp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm01immp.png&h=950d04ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eW9cqOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeW9cqOw.png&h=aa272afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去<br />\n1. 好up好濕，啲枕頭被套都好up<br />\n（我地亦預計應該係勁耐先換一次）<br />\n2. 所有野都好殘舊<br />\n3. 冷氣壞嘅<br />\n4. 風扇勁多塵<br />\n5. 冇毛巾冇水（水每次10000Vnd，3個幾Hkd）<br />\n6. 支洗頭水用左一半嘅<br />\n<br />\n不過我地冇怨過一句，反而覺得好Ok<br />\n49.5港幣一晚，仲想點？<br />\n當你冇期望，就唔會有失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c252ee20b63bb856b7cb94dc9f08a77f04fda1","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"Day2 (part 1) <br />\n「峴港開往順化的火車個景係咪真係咁靚？」<br />\n上網睇blog話個景好靚，<br />\n所以今日會喺峴港搭火車去順化，<br />\n本身九點幾去火車站買十二點幾嘅火車飛，<br />\n中間去下大教堂，周圍hea下<br />\n點知原來十點有班車，<br />\n望一望錶，已經九點二十五分。<br />\n距離酒店2.2km，仲未check out<br />\n好彩call左架grab，再叫佢喺酒店樓下等<br />\n終於喺九點五十五分上車。<br />\n費用96000VND（~35HKD），坐三個半鐘。<br />\n記住坐右邊，右邊先有海景睇<br />\n<br />\n架車入面係咁嘅：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZX14X6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZX14X6.png&h=07219358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車外嘅風景，一開始睇真係嘩嘩聲：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNOHPpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNOHPpV.png&h=dff3022f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQHadRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQHadRA.png&h=8091ffa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n架火車出面都幾靚幾復古：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkEG4Yn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkEG4Yn.png&h=309464d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實說個景真係唔錯，<br />\n但好似成程火車三個半鐘入面<br />\n都係得半個鐘係呢啲景<br />\n定係我瞓左？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過overall黎講都值得搭嘅"},{"pid":"a01c81fe2855b6c0a1b950c8c371536b09adf77c","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"Day2 - part2<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">「我竟然喺越南揸電單車」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n去到順化，我地住Anoma hotel<br />\n很推薦，88港幣一晚包早餐<br />\n服務態度非常好，好乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n我用自己個gps定位，<br />\ncall左grab去順化皇城。<br />\n但基於個定位原來唔準，<br />\n所以搞到個司機行錯左路，<br />\n最後佢黎到，黑晒面，好嬲<br />\n指住自己部電話，再指住我嗰部<br />\n之後周圍指，<br />\n意思係我搞到佢行錯路。<br />\n個重點係，之後佢唔肯開車<br />\n佢問我邊度黎，之後又怪責多我幾句<br />\n一路唔肯開車，但又唔係好出聲，<br />\n之後佢叫我俾我部電話佢，<br />\n我睬佢都傻，36計，1,2,3，<br />\n同老婆一齊開車門走人，<br />\n佢個眼神，幾驚佢拎枝槍出黎啪左我<br />\n（不過我知衰嘅，以後會入地址，<br />\nRather than用電話個自動定位）<br />\n<br />\n之後就再call唔到grab，<br />\n咁我咪唯有揸電單車去，<br />\n租電單車一日100000-150000VND<br />\n大概<span style=\"color: red;\">35-50</span>蚊一日，<br />\n我地嗰度係計24hrs，<br />\n但留意佢一俾你嘅時候係冇油嘅，<br />\n所以要即刻揸去油站入，<br />\n酒店reception就叫我地入50000VND<br />\n大概18蚊，應該起碼揸到40-50Km。<br />\n<br />\n一開始揸都未識驚，覺得幾好玩。<br />\n但越揸就越驚，最怕喺city揸車，<br />\n又多車又多彎，又成日要停車。<br />\n越揸越後悔，驚害到後面嗰個，<br />\n好彩最後攞到個竅門，<br />\n就係慢車嗰陣要雙腳伸直，<br />\n隨時放落地，<br />\n學識呢樣野之後就好好多了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dj3Ap0D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDj3Ap0D.png&h=4544d3d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxChDkF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxChDkF.png&h=1f1d641c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揸左大概其實都係around 10km<br />\n已經夠晒皮，可一不可再<br />\n你揸完你更加會好奇，<br />\n點解佢地咁亂都可以唔係成日發生意外<br />\n<br />\n奉勸各位喺越南揸電單車前真係要三思"},{"pid":"c98868168de2bb70aca1734e9da5ec3799363bbd","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:05:36.000Z","msg":"Day2 (part3) 完<br />\n<br />\n揸電單車去左順化皇城<br />\n去得順化，多數人都係去皇城皇陵<br />\n皇城入場費每人150000VND（53Hkd）<br />\n相比起當地消費都算貴<br />\n對於我地呢啲冇文化嘅入，<br />\n入去大概行1個鐘，影下相<br />\n皇城其實類似北京紫禁城<br />\n但入面幾寧靜幾peaceful<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kF1VvJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkF1VvJ2.png&h=9e2a033e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行完之後就返番Anoma hotel<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYDpo4C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYDpo4C.png&h=c74d2ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4VfvKD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4VfvKD.png&h=64ec8fbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c734464f2c3db4c60d83c4f009fd208d30ebde94","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"Day3 (part1)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">順化 -&gt; 會安</span><br />\n<br />\n成日都落雨，<br />\n都唔敢再揸電單車周圍去，<br />\n等今日下午1pm嘅巴士去會安（Hoi An），<br />\n打過幾間價，最平大概80000VND（28Hkd）<br />\n大概坐4-5個鐘<br />\n<br />\n酒店其實乜都會幫到你買/book，<br />\n但要食啲佣所以費用一定貴，佢收5USD<br />\n<br />\n12點半就會有van黎酒店pick up你，<br />\n載埋其他人就會去大巴站，<br />\n喺酒店千祈唔好遲到，<br />\n否則成車人就要等你一兩個人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e4SajHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4SajHw.png&h=3838b610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n架車係咁嘅，<br />\n有個窿俾你伸腳同放少少野<br />\n呢個時候好慶幸自己生得唔高<br />\n圖中嗰個鬼佬目測兩米零六<br />\n隻腳長到隊唔入，長期要放出黎<br />\n睇見就辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/17/162304_08d77967d105076dd338e7083dbd27ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F17%2F162304_08d77967d105076dd338e7083dbd27ad.png&h=c3c820f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2FnVfU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2FnVfU.png&h=cd79157c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上車要除鞋，十足十入啲日本旅館<br />\n差啲講左句O hai yo gor zai e ma su<br />\n司機會俾個膠袋你袋住對鞋<br />\n好似好乾淨<br />\n實質架車都幾污糟，枕頭應該十年冇換<br />\n不嬲安全意識高，喺香港都會纜安全帶<br />\n我個位咁啱個扣爛左，<br />\n唯有希望平平安安"},{"pid":"28e2ec9db560b70c2c510a51adad30bbc2230dcc","tid":983834,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"d4b75543c5bbc2f1c9f681e51f5c51ca3600c794","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"Day3 (part2) 完<br />\n會安古城<br />\n<br />\n落左車都差不多天黑<br />\n有啲肚餓，就去左食banh my queen<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GK2Yvmv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGK2Yvmv.png&h=91b68ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/17/213732_0ddd15624fb123312873acc09aba5054.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F17%2F213732_0ddd15624fb123312873acc09aba5054.png&h=a9e9c6b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbanh my係去越南必食嘅野<br />\n又平好又食，類似法包<br />\n包左啲肉、酸菜、生菜、？豬肝醬<br />\n（個人唔吃豬肝，但陣味唔會食得出）<br />\n每個大概15000-30000VND(6-10Hkd)<br />\n<br />\n食完就去check in再出去古城行下<br />\n會安古城晚晚都係中秋節<br />\n成個氣氛都好好feel<br />\n一街都係燈籠<br />\n啲餐廳都會裝飾到自己間野好靚<br />\n（個人唯一一個唔中意會安嘅地方<br />\n就係呢度太旅遊區，所有野都比出面貴<br />\n同埋少左一片寧靜，成日會有sell你野）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得會安嘅夜晚比日頭吸引好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyXxzP4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyXxzP4.png&h=3a8fe88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzs5UQr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuzs5UQr.png&h=18cc41c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有機會一定要同女朋友黎下，<br />\n如果你有。"},{"pid":"169e920129f8932e057ca5dbe1fc4679d3a68588","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"Day 4,5 完<br />\n<br />\n不停落雨<br />\n本身想去玩bamboo boat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知仲有冇其他地方有得玩呢<br />\n除左出去隔離街食野都冇去景點<br />\n唯有喺酒店plan二月去南美嘅行程<br />\n<br />\n呢間叫the kebab shack<br />\n其實我覺得叫貴，食個意粉要40蚊<br />\n唯獨個pork kebab加薯角扺食，28蚊<br />\n有啲燒豬肉加埋生菜仲有酸蘿蔔<br />\n好開胃<br />\n薯角好熱好大份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7an2jqE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7an2jqE.png&h=c4589304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83x9JSm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83x9JSm.png&h=f2d7ba86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再去食左碗Cao Lao，高樓麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvRKxM8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvRKxM8.png&h=1e012c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窮人恩物，30000VND(11蚊有找)<br />\n高樓麵係會安特產，<br />\n我個人唔太中意啲麵質，一咬即爛<br />\n冇乜口感<br />\n啲餸就有炸豬皮、叉燒（Ok好味架喎）<br />\n仲有啲生菜and herbs<br />\n<br />\n會安特色小食主要有：<br />\n1. Cao Lau<br />\n2. white rose （個人覺得好普通）<br />\n係豬肉餃子，但皮好厚，舊豬肉重胡椒味<br />\n3. 炸雲吞（太熱氣冇食）<br />\n4. 仲有兩三樣，但冇乜興趣所以冇食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚將會搭13個鐘夜巴去大叻 Da Lat<br />\n越南人嘅避暑勝地"},{"pid":"dcd3d3387f82b3f6580eb12cc68af109a68560ac","tid":983834,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"Live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71bbf0e37f63021fa43f810f20b561bc8442231","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"Day6 (part1)<br />\n「坐夜巴去大叻」<br />\n<br />\n我地坐喺會安去大叻嘅夜巴<br />\n全程13個鐘<br />\n<br />\n大巴18:00開車<br />\n但17:00要喺酒店lobby等pick up<br />\n<br />\n就係呢啲小型van<br />\n個司機會周圍接人去巴士總站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEAOZDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEAOZDu.png&h=20ad4a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要塞到爆晒先可以開車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppVzaLE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppVzaLE.png&h=d08dd548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚嗰架大巴好唔正經<br />\n好似大陸啲螢光剪髮鋪按摩鋪咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcZ8fcH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcZ8fcH.png&h=f12349e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大巴係先上先揀位<br />\n我仲以為啲鬼會好唔care先後<br />\n點知佢地都係同我一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEzTrjE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEzTrjE.png&h=5d4aff86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全車有九成幾係鬼妹鬼仔<br />\n大概一成係越南人<br />\n仲有兩個就係我同我老婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揀位最緊要兩樣野：<br />\n1. 坐凳可以pop up（當你瞓唔著但都要你瞓平其實真係好辛苦，我嗰張就係pop up制壞左，我成晚都平瞓，望住車頂眼光光，條頸頸痛，不過要同老婆一齊坐，所以都冇得調位）<br />\n2. 有安全帶！超緊要<br />\n啲夜巴司機仲激過紅van司機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aN3drj9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaN3drj9.png&h=5c535805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於啲喺車睇書玩電話唔會頭暈嘅人黎講<br />\n13個鐘好快過<br />\n但我係一睇就會想嘔<br />\n成晚難捱，望住個鐘成晚<br />\n<br />\n個司機一路揸，完全冇停嘅意慾<br />\n我個肚打晒鼓，上一餐係一點食<br />\n佢最後十點先停車<br />\n會停喺佢指定嘅鋪頭<br />\n有時會係油站food court，有時係餐廳<br />\n我估有佣收<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GxatAt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GxatAt.png&h=92275964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁冇質素嘅雞肉方便麵<br />\n雞肉幾好味<br />\n但個麵十足十小學小食部嗰啲<br />\n擺個麵，加熱水，俾個蓋你<br />\n自己慢慢焗<br />\n但我實在太肚餓，佢未林我已經食完<br />\n咁都收我50000VND(18蚊)<br />\n平時一碗牛河都係30000VND<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVOXS2M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVOXS2M.png&h=4212e759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜巴嘅車頭相<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDMKx3R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDMKx3R.png&h=d64b70a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺夜巴我勸你地都係<br />\n眼不見為安全<br />\n成車瞓晒，得我眼光光望住司機揸車<br />\n條路雙線雙程，中間冇野隔住<br />\n夜晚清一色都係長車<br />\n一係貨車一係旅遊大巴<br />\n我睇住個司機長期突左半架車過隔離<br />\n狂超越其他大車<br />\n有時見佢跟住前面架旅遊巴過架大貨車<br />\n好驚前面過到我地就撞對頭車<br />\n<br />\n有時間中見對頭有車就縮番個頭入去<br />\n我望住我老婆個安全帶扣，係壞嘅<br />\n嗰次係我第一次想用繩綁住我老婆<br />\n<br />\n到早上七點終於到大叻了<br />\n揸到咁先準時到達<br />\n如果安全啲咁揸會幾點到"},{"pid":"f3f6bd8016cc0c2570fd5fb89f523b5d8f65028d","tid":983834,"uid":151436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a49f76cb5adf838910b4c08e05165c71825ad67","tid":983834,"uid":73381,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"雞肉方便麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬支那仔confirmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dfd00adaab52b2fe293acd58baad2f8774822f","tid":983834,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921628d12c88ebba1a6d32f6519860f63cb838a5","tid":983834,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"做乜唔返工？ 一陣比hr問你做乜有空窗期"},{"pid":"999e7731cd52b5a754c621a9ea2e0edc394427bc","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"3a49f76cb5adf838910b4c08e05165c71825ad67","tid":983834,"uid":73381,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"雞肉方便麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬支那仔confirmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:37:54.000Z","msg":"我仲有去左揸機車添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dedcf79bc63e3acdfb47c296e806fb552b075d","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921628d12c88ebba1a6d32f6519860f63cb838a5","tid":983834,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"做乜唔返工？ 一陣比hr問你做乜有空窗期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"話freelance囉😂希望唔好穿煲"},{"pid":"51a0e50bb97b01b71d1dcd027d13e504a483dc87","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"Day6 大叻 (part 1) <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「大叻瑪利亞修道院」</span><br />\n<br />\n其實2013年都黎過大叻<br />\n覺得呢度幾舒服幾唔似越南（冇咁亂）<br />\n天氣又涼浸浸，around 十幾度<br />\n但都係冇乜驚天動地嘅景點架喇<br />\n不過老婆未黎過，都想帶下佢黎<br />\n<br />\n落左夜巴，早上七點正<br />\n成晚瞓得三個鐘，好攰好冇精神<br />\n最緊要係頭又lup口又臭<br />\n都冇乜心情去玩<br />\n我幾年前黎過東南亞玩2x日<br />\n印象中瞓完night bus，<br />\n通常如果酒店有空房都會俾你早入住<br />\n所以會早上七八點就check in<br />\n瞓到十一二點就出去玩<br />\n點知今日佢話未有房要14:00先入得<br />\n我地兩呆左，點hea六個鐘<br />\n<br />\n最後都係死死地氣<br />\n好似玩完ocamp第二日咁出去玩<br />\n我地成日都係今日搵聽日後日行程<br />\n加上我黎過，所以都冇乜prep過<br />\n<br />\n竟然誤打誤撞去左個幾靚嘅修道院<br />\n影左幾張自己覺得幾靚嘅相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJOUbXN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJOUbXN.png&h=0205fa60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaTg9Kt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaTg9Kt.png&h=4c3d98c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMcJPKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMcJPKv.png&h=2217e4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面幾寧靜，個人入到去好舒服<br />\n應該影下相都夠你行半個鐘嘅"},{"pid":"c9f922496eaad7cd0e6d7182d058fdd71bd611e8","tid":983834,"uid":41908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b695ea40070554e0e8ec4dad5a907784d05729","tid":983834,"uid":81383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"幾好睇 期待你更新"},{"pid":"e5a4a84eaa1bcac230372e6c5b331fb6bbc2f07a","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88b695ea40070554e0e8ec4dad5a907784d05729","tid":983834,"uid":81383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"幾好睇 期待你更新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"Thz<br />\n聽日繼續up下大叻景點<br />\n其實我比較期待之後去緬甸老撾<br />\n到時可以同大家分享下"},{"pid":"af268b66e157c5b4f8cff9a05a7a0d9f14b6fe39","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"Day6 大叻 (part2)<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">市內亂行一通</span><br />\n<br />\n之後就喺附近周圍行下<br />\n影下相<br />\n<br />\n喺Da Lat Market某個位影落去<br />\n睇到嗰時覺得個畫面好亂<br />\n但攝影功力有限<br />\n影唔到嗰個feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Vjj8k0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Vjj8k0.png&h=4902caf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exsJQzZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexsJQzZ.png&h=5024ab37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDa Lat market嗰個迴旋處<br />\n我覺得係地標黎<br />\n其實都唔知係唔係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fdZ0SOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfdZ0SOq.png&h=5fa25173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbriEt3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbriEt3.png&h=3cbcb40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時去東南亞就係中意影呢啲<br />\n呢啲唔係喺日本可以影到嘅感覺<br />\n（自問攝影技術九流，好依賴外在個景）<br />\n一去到日本就好似唔想拎部相機出黎咁"},{"pid":"13f148a4c74a03a222f47bb6cb71ebc43a38d2ce","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T17:30:26.000Z","msg":"Day6 大叻（Part3）<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">「今次唔揸電單車，揸雙人車」</span><br />\n<br />\n自從上次喺順化揸過電單車之後<br />\n始終有少少驚<br />\n驚在個油門控制得唔好，會失平衡pk<br />\n<br />\n咁啱俾我見到呢架野，<br />\n喺大迴轉處隔離有檔單車鋪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esrOhj4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FesrOhj4.png&h=a058adb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我問老闆要幾錢，11點踩到6pm就70000VND<br />\n大概25蚊左右<br />\n個老闆sell我租綿羊仔，150000VND<br />\n仲要俾錢入油，成200000VND，70蚊<br />\n一黎我淆底（單車個速度易控制好多）<br />\n二黎想慳啲錢<br />\n不過我問老闆全日租幾錢，六點還又幾錢<br />\n佢兩次都要load成幾秒先答到我<br />\n令我覺得佢有少少想掠我多啲咁<br />\n定我份人太攻心計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過架車都好一般<br />\n個後brake壞嘅，冇轉波<br />\n前軚唔夠氣<br />\nsit位冇得調，屈住隻腳踩點發力<br />\n但嗰時心急一攞車就走<br />\n是Q但啦你俾乜我我踩乜啦<br />\n最弊連鎖都冇問佢借/租<br />\n去到景點都唔知點算<br />\n仲要俾佢收左証件，架車冇左我實gg<br />\n（我已經唔俾passport佢，俾回鄉證佢）<br />\n<br />\n好彩有個鎖喺身用黎鎖斜揹袋嘅<br />\n頂住當先<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnvvvG9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnvvvG9.png&h=7958a03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連入cafe飲野都要睇住架車<br />\n不停用支zoom鏡黎睇車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ze8hnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ze8hnM.png&h=13bc7b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪仲難搵過威利<br />\n<br />\n去火車站途中<br />\n見到兩舊野<br />\n1. Doha Cafe<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/080WrgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F080WrgG.png&h=72c54aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面啲野飲多數都貴過40000VND<br />\n<br />\n2. 好似係shopping mall黎<br />\n但我有架單車喺手<br />\n費事入去睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnjoQKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnjoQKe.png&h=bca66e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有啲湖景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kg6KAbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkg6KAbk.png&h=1857a01a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一part就會講<br />\n我之後踩左成6,7km<br />\n去Sunny Cafe（天梯打卡位）<br />\n<br />\n同埋會up少少夜市相<br />\n聽日再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849a610e2c3cd0ae5f1b54bebdac13ef9df1e5f1","tid":983834,"uid":223611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T18:35:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d7acaddc9c0c033e58f3ec09863cede3c38e6264","tid":983834,"uid":166239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左柬埔寨簽證未，你打算係越南搵旅行社整定自己上網搞?<br />\np.s.人在清邁，下星期會去柬埔寨，因為唔知係咪一定要準確入境日期，所以仲未整簽證😞"},{"pid":"78ee6439116d807e9a9cecfc69d5c235cc2a725f","tid":983834,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7acaddc9c0c033e58f3ec09863cede3c38e6264","tid":983834,"uid":166239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左柬埔寨簽證未，你打算係越南搵旅行社整定自己上網搞?<br />\np.s.人在清邁，下星期會去柬埔寨，因為唔知係咪一定要準確入境日期，所以仲未整簽證😞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T22:41:30.000Z","msg":"日期應該要準確<br />\n<br />\n樓主依家人係邊？同遊記差幾多日"},{"pid":"0ac76561e5f63e363e3a6beef7e2a8e040c99d0d","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7acaddc9c0c033e58f3ec09863cede3c38e6264","tid":983834,"uid":166239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左柬埔寨簽證未，你打算係越南搵旅行社整定自己上網搞?<br />\np.s.人在清邁，下星期會去柬埔寨，因為唔知係咪一定要準確入境日期，所以仲未整簽證😞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T01:10:28.000Z","msg":"未呀，之後去嗰啲地方全部都搞落地簽<br />\n我陸路過柬埔寨，胡志明去金邊<br />\n多數你真實入境日期遲過你報嗰個入境日期都ok架喎<br />\n其實好多人都冇可能咁準確<br />\n不過我想慳番網上搞嗰幾蚊美金<br />\n所以直接落地搞算<br />\n睇人地啲blog好似都ok架喎"},{"pid":"904ac92210dad489232deb438707efcdb82af11e","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78ee6439116d807e9a9cecfc69d5c235cc2a725f","tid":983834,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7acaddc9c0c033e58f3ec09863cede3c38e6264","tid":983834,"uid":166239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整左柬埔寨簽證未，你打算係越南搵旅行社整定自己上網搞?<br />\np.s.人在清邁，下星期會去柬埔寨，因為唔知係咪一定要準確入境日期，所以仲未整簽證😞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T22:41:30.000Z","msg":"日期應該要準確<br />\n<br />\n樓主依家人係邊？同遊記差幾多日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"仲喺大叻<br />\n差半日"},{"pid":"4053a9f258c0302ef92dc9696e77c44d41274ede","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"剛剛去完美奈沙漠日出tour<br />\n真係好正<br />\n好似係去咁多日越南最正嘅回憶<br />\n晏啲希望會打番個遊記<br />\n<br />\n其實咁長篇咁打十幾日遊記好似好悶<br />\n自己都冇乜耐性睇番<br />\n其實係咪轉打遊記散文會比較好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc0d68cdad5b3e58acf053bb1fdd6db8e2adf8d","tid":983834,"uid":81383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"詳細d幾好啊 呢d地方 我完全唔會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24708cb0732788c53fdc83e1083a53d7944db65","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fc0d68cdad5b3e58acf053bb1fdd6db8e2adf8d","tid":983834,"uid":81383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"詳細d幾好啊 呢d地方 我完全唔會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"知道有人睇自己個post其實真係幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就係覺得太詳細啲人都冇乜心機睇<br />\n<br />\n唔會去嘅地方都有興趣睇架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而比較中意睇啲自己將會去嘅地方"},{"pid":"be06e7ab19900efca60b2ff63770ad0c66b100dd","tid":983834,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a24708cb0732788c53fdc83e1083a53d7944db65","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fc0d68cdad5b3e58acf053bb1fdd6db8e2adf8d","tid":983834,"uid":81383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"詳細d幾好啊 呢d地方 我完全唔會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"知道有人睇自己個post其實真係幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就係覺得太詳細啲人都冇乜心機睇<br />\n<br />\n唔會去嘅地方都有興趣睇架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而比較中意睇啲自己將會去嘅地方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"想睇樓豬返支那吃方便麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7956d0f1ce53c4afb12df43842a02c413462ae65","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be06e7ab19900efca60b2ff63770ad0c66b100dd","tid":983834,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a24708cb0732788c53fdc83e1083a53d7944db65","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fc0d68cdad5b3e58acf053bb1fdd6db8e2adf8d","tid":983834,"uid":81383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"詳細d幾好啊 呢d地方 我完全唔會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"知道有人睇自己個post其實真係幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就係覺得太詳細啲人都冇乜心機睇<br />\n<br />\n唔會去嘅地方都有興趣睇架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而比較中意睇啲自己將會去嘅地方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"想睇樓豬返支那吃方便麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"咁應該冇乜機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對上一次返去好似係去雲南玩<br />\n十年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0874380434cfdcaf7c3eea6beab7ee4fc959d159","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"本身都冇乜心機再打落去<br />\n好似冇乜人睇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點都會打埋呢篇美奈遊記<br />\n因為始終係自己黎左越南九日<br />\n最開心最充實嘅moment<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由大叻 去 美奈<br />\n搭~5個鐘車，啲路超多彎<br />\n又勁凳，坐到成車人嘩嘩聲<br />\n呢個地方主要係得一條大街<br />\n成條街都係沿海<br />\n成條街都係食海鮮<br />\n望住個海聽住海浪聲食海鮮都咪話唔爽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16S99rZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16S99rZ.png&h=2ff17b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話少講<br />\n夜晚去左食下啲平價海鮮<br />\n我地揀左啲最平嘅食<br />\n貴嗰啲當然冇我份（eg龍蝦，百幾蚊）<br />\n揀左小扇貝同蝦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opSaTUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopSaTUu.png&h=feab8766&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/21/225455_df3fea98febb3da71b51520d016df7b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2F225455_df3fea98febb3da71b51520d016df7b9.png&h=c099190e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n扇貝 40000vnd（14hkd）有二十隻<br />\n蝦 85000vnd （30hkd）<br />\n<br />\n啲材料唔係新鮮嘅，但食落都幾好肉質<br />\n但個烹調方法真係好一般<br />\n勁重味勁油完全冇晒海鮮鮮味<br />\n（可能係我錯啦揀左garlic butter）<br />\n令我第二日都冇再食海鮮嘅意慾<br />\n<br />\n轉頭打埋第日去日出tour<br />\n妖點解打黎打去都未入正題<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eda15fc2f3353adff6dab4b9ccd71854da871c1","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">「美奈日出團」</span><br />\n<br />\n費用: 1200000vnd（420hkd）<br />\n都幾貴，但值得嘅<br />\n時間：04:30-08:30am<br />\n包：<br />\n- private jeep 2人團<br />\n- 喺白沙漠揸atv 20分鐘<br />\n- 喺白沙丘坐atv上高處睇日出<br />\n- 所有入場費（不過本身都係三兩萬）<br />\n<br />\n行程<br />\n1. White sand dune看日出<br />\n（距離市區30k）<br />\n2. red sand dune<br />\n3. 漁村<br />\n4. 仙女溪 Fairy stream<br />\n<br />\n天都未光就要起身出去睇日出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQA0wQt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQA0wQt.png&h=f9fc3624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\njeep其實一啲都唔好坐<br />\n避震又差（可能我地嗰架頹）<br />\n又勁大風，吹到人都癲"},{"pid":"d312677a377902afc61b1ff5f7fd43e88dd1d72d","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"成班atv喺度接客<br />\n車人上山丘睇日出<br />\n唔坐都得，不過行上去可能都半粒鐘<br />\n加上啲沙勁鬆勁軟<br />\n喺上面行真係勁攰<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/21/232558_6bbe722ef2b6d13109e68cfa5760a07c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2F232558_6bbe722ef2b6d13109e68cfa5760a07c.png&h=1fc336a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次坐atv，驚到pk<br />\n又冇安全帶條友又懶型咁揸勁快<br />\n我同老婆同佢一架車<br />\n我坐最後，我幾驚俾佢拋左出車<br />\n俾佢搶走左我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺山丘上面比想像中冇乜風<br />\n幾平靜<br />\n直至越黎越多遊客黎<br />\n其實覺得泡菜妹真係好鬼嘈<br />\n不過見佢地幾靚就算啦<br />\n<br />\n等到最後都係冇咸蛋黃睇<br />\n得呢啲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0XVkM2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0XVkM2.png&h=2f584377&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbwyRTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbwyRTL.png&h=21b613c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經坐喺度影<br />\n但硬係有啲人好似透明咁<br />\n係咁衝去最前影<br />\n仲要擺埋啲咁嘅pose<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9TpYzd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9TpYzd.png&h=c274a222&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnpXy7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnpXy7A.png&h=762a336e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完就上atv<br />\n首先係個哥哥仔載我地先<br />\n嗰度有個目測60度嘅斜路<br />\n我真係估唔到佢會喺嗰度衝落去<br />\n衝嗰時我勁想求佢停<br />\n但衝完又覺得好爽<br />\n<br />\n落左去之後就到我地揸<br />\n個人覺得坐仲好玩過自己揸<br />\n我揸到勁chok<br />\n有一下個哥哥都差啲跌左落車<br />\n搞到之後佢都成日要捉住我隻手黎揸<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/21/233906_f3a503e697750ed88ba41506b259835c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2F233906_f3a503e697750ed88ba41506b259835c.png&h=e509c1f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unnNWnP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunnNWnP.png&h=6de80e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完之後就去左Red sand dune<br />\n呢度細過white sand dune好多<br />\n不過啲沙紅紅地<br />\n我覺得影相會靚過白沙漠嗰度<br />\n呢度冇atv玩，不過有得滑沙<br />\n啲人會係咁過黎sell你<br />\n<br />\n光天化日都咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUpHLg7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUpHLg7.png&h=e71c2381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有人玩人形蜈蚣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJOA5hE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJOA5hE.png&h=e30e6df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大嬸一野加速<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7yUBpp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7yUBpp.png&h=fed623b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFailed<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XANKebe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXANKebe.png&h=ad0113cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完呢度就去左漁村<br />\n睇下都幾靚，但冇乜特別<br />\n所以影左幾張相就走左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ifzBqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ifzBqo.png&h=d94c7c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPvS7w7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPvS7w7.png&h=f4aba497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就去左仙女溪<br />\n呢度啲沙都幾幼<br />\n不過間中都有野幾吉腳<br />\n要小心行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXeBq8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXeBq8.png&h=21e71598&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvUc7xT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvUc7xT.png&h=6b909a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見巴打咁捧場睇到呢度<br />\n俾大家睇下我喺仙女溪見到嘅仙女<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gbt5H69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbt5H69.png&h=564d656d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個美奈都係呢啲jeep<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/btimgsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbtimgsM.png&h=59eb5bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ze4wDF9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fze4wDF9.png&h=63ca635f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmQ0w1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmQ0w1c.png&h=1251af34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gs4sWsV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGs4sWsV.png&h=7a295054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得美奈真係值得黎<br />\n可能因為前幾日喺越南真係幾悶<br />\n所以呢度比到少少驚喜我<br />\n加上仙女溪真係好正，i mean啲女<br />\n所以下次黎越南就考慮下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed96786c6f2e9fe259e32de46b08c1eae35e49ef","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"再貼多兩張喺美奈沙灘影嘅夕陽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYHqOdn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYHqOdn.png&h=3f870c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDDp3MK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDDp3MK.png&h=9f771a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度嘅巴打<br />\n可否留個名當係支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62ac4e502f44261b44e5e8709347d7caa0d28b3","tid":983834,"uid":151436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"加油 繼續打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ee85c9c89c58620b78031aadf6a291fbe31db1","tid":983834,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62ac4e502f44261b44e5e8709347d7caa0d28b3","tid":983834,"uid":151436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"加油 繼續打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"Thz巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日離開越南嚕<br />\n<br />\n之後可能會開第二個post<br />\n打下柬埔寨緬甸老撾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1bdbfdd86e7e3780b15439734afa373fd28c92","tid":983834,"uid":166562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\